2. 问题: 分析不同员工处理的支付中，金额分布区间（<3元、3-6元、>6元）的笔数占比
   原始错误: trailing junk after numeric literal 在 "3至6元笔数" 或附近的
LINE 1: ...UNT(*) FILTER (WHERE p.amount BETWEEN 3 AND 6) AS 3至6元笔数...
                                                             ^
   修复后SQL:
   SELECT s.first_name || ' ' || s.last_name AS "员工姓名", COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE p.amount < 3) AS "小于3元笔数", COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE p.amount >= 3 AND p.amount <= 6) AS "3至6元笔数", COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE p.amount > 6) AS "大于6元笔数", ROUND(100.0 * COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE p.amount < 3) / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0), 2) AS "小于3元占比", ROUND(100.0 * COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE p.amount >= 3 AND p.amount <= 6) / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0), 2) AS "3至6元占比", ROUND(100.0 * COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE p.amount > 6) / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0), 2) AS "大于6元占比" FROM public.payment p JOIN public.staff s ON p.staff_id = s.staff_id GROUP BY s.staff_id, s.first_name, s.last_name ORDER BY "员工姓名";
